=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75c2b9398153fe95db8e777294fb6c8a63e0dbf","tid":498762,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/144448_34d9e2e53019a97df303120a7aaf0216.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F14%2F144448_34d9e2e53019a97df303120a7aaf0216.jpg&h=967b9ccc&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n毒撚去到邊都得唔到保障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a818fde8b143206a952a9faad6b135321b8095d4","tid":498762,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"家暴受害者忍氣吞聲好出奇咩<br />\n分分鐘有斯德哥爾摩症侯群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a581f01a239f334a23f991dcf122a8f9211aa147","tid":498762,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"香港地有塊閪真係無撚敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係無撚敵呀！！！"},{"pid":"aa551d638362ce40af2e400043085a7bc5ccfbb1","tid":498762,"uid":10788,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"事主身型魁梧，要制止34歲纖瘦女被告伍寧頤的多番嚴重襲擊，本來毫無難度，但事主竟選擇忍氣吞聲，不懂走避，證供有違常理，匪夷所思，並不可信<br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣得？？屌呀"},{"pid":"33dbf27fd8048a8817dd981a5e4791b9172eebb6","tid":498762,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"白痴 影衰晒男人"},{"pid":"66376aa3fb00c50f3a9caaed7249ebeba758286f","tid":498762,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線... 係咪條仔自己係法庭招認咗有M系性癖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a885373e499bc4c27eb0aae81e2baf55e73e9576","tid":498762,"uid":59695,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:03:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.judiciary.hk/en/crt_lists/lists/14122017/dc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fen%2Fcrt_lists%2Flists%2F14122017%2Fdc.html&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4e01e514\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.judiciary.hk/en/crt_lists/lists/14122017/dc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n陳慧敏<br />\n區域法院  暫委法官<br />\nDeputy District Judge<br />\nAmy Chan<br />\n<br />\n女法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07119f5b834d8c383e44c6a2bd88688aed294805","tid":498762,"uid":139401,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無業獨居男疑遇上惡港女，見女方稱無處容身而收留，怎料兩人由相伴聊天煮飯仔演變成虐待收場。港女疑將投資股票失利責任歸咎於獨居男，要他到廢鐵回收店做「苦工」賺錢還給她；後來男方被炒，她涉以沸水淋潑洩憤，又怪責他煮食不合口味，以菜刀刀背及刀柄擊打其頭、眉心和面，令他門牙脫落、頭頂流血，直至要追看電視劇《武則天》才停手。案件今於區院裁決，港女被告獲判兩罪罪名不成立。被告於庭外表示，對裁決結果「冇乜開心唔開心」，但感謝代表大狀顧佩芳的協助。<br />\n<br />\n法官於裁決書中指出，43歲事主林志華庭上證供與其口供紙內容多處不相符。事主身型魁梧，要制止34歲纖瘦女被告伍寧頤的多番嚴重襲擊，本來毫無難度，但事主竟選擇忍氣吞聲，不懂走避，證供有違常理，匪夷所思，並不可信，故裁定女被告脫罪。法庭並下令被告兼獲訟費。<br />\n報稱曾留學澳洲、樣貌標緻、身材高䠷的被告伍寧頤，早前否認有意圖而導致他人身體受傷害及襲擊致造成傷害兩罪。聆訊期間，她曾在男友及親友陪同下到庭受審，<span style=\"color: red;\">男友全程抱着粉紅身、金色腳的獨角獸手袋旁聽。</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8802ea8d34280b08d67a9e3836a9fd5ec9246bd","tid":498762,"uid":139401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/14/144448_34d9e2e53019a97df303120a7aaf0216.jpg\" data-thum