d":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"可唔可以上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒撚好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a4d8a8f2414e767c1bbbb6e672dce8493c65a2","tid":498762,"uid":55391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開埋名<br />\n<br />\n個女仔冇曬前途啦</blockquote><br />\n咁既樣怕咩"},{"pid":"5be921ed785766aa9eb7fb291d3a266c0cd65d6d","tid":498762,"uid":60219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.judiciary.hk/en/crt_lists/lists/14122017/dc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.judiciary.hk%2Fen%2Fcrt_lists%2Flists%2F14122017%2Fdc.html&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=4e01e514\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.judiciary.hk/en/crt_lists/lists/14122017/dc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n陳慧敏<br />\n區域法院  暫委法官<br />\nDeputy District Judge<br />\nAmy Chan<br />\n<br />\n女法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女法官本身無問題，但係弱智既女法官就好有問題，佢以前就比人屌過佢斷章取義誤解判詞<br />\n<br />\n賄賂案 誤解供詞 亂判被告有罪<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110603/00176_002.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20110603%2F00176_002.html&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=05d2e85b\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20110603/00176_002.html</a><br />\n杜麗冰昨在判詞指，控方的主要證供來自污點證人指證，原審裁判官信納其證供，並於判決時以被告的警誡供詞作為支持污點證人證供的佐證。但杜官指<span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官錯誤理解了警誡供詞的內容，她舉例指，被告曾在警誡供詞中提及「早出」的做法，裁判官便認為，此段供詞印證了污點證人指被告受賄後准許遺體「早出」。但其實被告在警誡供詞中，純粹指出有上司會容許「早出」的行為，跟受賄與否根本無關。</span>"},{"pid":"c12